From 0000000000000000000000000000000000000006 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Boot Debug <noreply@qti.qualcomm.com>
Date: Mon, 30 Jun 2026 00:00:00 +0000
Subject: [DEV] qcom-distro-catchall.yml: build only proprietary image

The catchall distro defines its own target list (overriding qcom-distro.yml),
so the dev-speedup must also be applied here. Comment out multimedia and
container-orchestration so a --catchall build only produces
qcom-multimedia-proprietary-image. Drop to restore the full list.

Upstream-Status: Inappropriate [local dev speedup]
---
diff --git a/ci/qcom-distro-catchall.yml b/ci/qcom-distro-catchall.yml
index c63a2303..51d170dd 100644
--- a/ci/qcom-distro-catchall.yml
+++ b/ci/qcom-distro-catchall.yml
@@ -8,6 +8,6 @@ header:
 distro: qcom-distro-catchall
 
 target:
-  - qcom-multimedia-image
+  # - qcom-multimedia-image            # disabled: build only proprietary image to speed up dev
   - qcom-multimedia-proprietary-image
-  - qcom-container-orchestration-image
+  # - qcom-container-orchestration-image  # disabled
